<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ل ز ج<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٤٥٥٨ - ل ز ج]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>تلزَّجَ يتلزَّج، تلزُّجًا، فهو مُتلزِّج<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• تلزَّج الشَّيءُ:</span> صار لزِجًا يَلْصَق بعضُه ببعض.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• تلزَّج الشَّعَرُ:</span> تلبَّد من الوَسَخ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>